  <li>Say where you have tried to look for an answer - people wonâ€™t point you towards the same resource, so youâ€™re not wasting anybodyâ€™s time</li>
  <li>Suggest what direction youâ€™d take next and even ask if one of them might be the right one - it shows youâ€™re thinking about the problem and that you try to be an active participant in finding the solution</li>
